{"tid":1577702,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"（陰謀論） 如果呢個時候，中共搵人老強某黑警個女","createTime":"2019-09-17T23:55:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-17T23:56:34.000Z","uid":93588,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"5adf11dffabd165288f4a77038017ac1f6d9fb0e","tid":1577702,"uid":93588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T23:55:25.000Z","msg":"話要為新屋嶺被集體老強嘅女仔報仇，點拆？<br />\n<br />\n先用假消息煲大新屋嶺事件，再屈示威者私了強姦，用返一貫嘅叫雞套餐玩人格毀滅，都好有佢哋風格。<br />\n<br />\n利申<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/tongue.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 信新屋嶺有打人濫權，唔信所有強姦消息，好鬼。"},{"pid":"e2c6c3f8c98c3a981739ea01075525f72eb04f16","tid":1577702,"uid":61484,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T23:56:34.000Z","msg":"不割"}]}